                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>The color of the balance of the mongrel ticket is not stated. Verily, the
                    abolitionist are fast approaching their end, and if the New Yorkers only give
                    them sufficient rope, they will hang themselves.</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Announces abolitionist nomination in New York elections.</summary>
